<meta name="sailthru.title" content="This Is How Your Fat Friend Feels When You Say You’re Concerned for Their Health" />
<meta name="sailthru.date" content="2016-04-08T07:00:00-04:00" />
<link href="http://greatist.com/live/how-your-fat-friend-feels-when-you-say-youre-concerned-for-their-health" rel="canonical" />
