        ><span itemprop="name">Your Fat Friend</span>
        </a>
      </span>
    </div>
          </div>
          <h1 class="title" id="page-title" itemprop="name headline alternativeHeadline">This Is How Your Fat Friend Feels When You Say You’re Concerned for Their Health</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="top-share">
          <div class="group_share" data-recirc-section>
  <div class="share-buttons icons" data-origin="top">
    <div ng-controller="socialCtrl"
